Package com.flipkart.bean

Class SlotDetails

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.bean.SlotDetails
public class SlotDetails extends Object
The SlotDetails class represents the details of a slot in a gym. It includes information such as the slot ID, gym ID, date, start and end times, number of seats, and seats left.
